{"tid":1709911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭取消自己活動：安全理由　林鄭槍林彈雨叫學生返學：唔好中計","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:30:33.000Z","uid":82640,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"093fde3b0addde09eadfd5f41688a1d830cf08b6","tid":1709911,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭用安全理由長年唔出黎見扑咪唔開工照出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打工仔學生食哂催淚彈返工返學冇得避叫做唔好中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己仔女去德國嘆世界，人地啲仔女唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲每次期待林奠出黎救火，就見到佢真．為香港加油，加下奠油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人問啲簡單問題都駁唔到，發幾句爛渣就塞返入寫字樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衰過清朝，廢過慈禧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a922f0be96e85a3728e79057843cdec0c4504d5","tid":1709911,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b4af8dd5d12ec329fb5f71e7c94b00a083fa2b0","tid":1709911,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"文宣做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823bceb8766d48faa7b17522e66d09dcd18aa474","tid":1709911,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b4af8dd5d12ec329fb5f71e7c94b00a083fa2b0","tid":1709911,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"文宣做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply